HEADWORD: Unappropriate
<hw>Un`ap*pro"pri*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>un-</ets> not + <ets>appropriate</ets>, a.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Inappropriate; unsuitable.</def>⟦br⟧
