==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unappropriate
<hw>Un`ap*pro"pri*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st
pref. <ets>un-</ets> + <ets>appropriate</ets>, v. t.]</ety> <def>To take
from private possession; to restore to the possession or right of all;
<as>as, to <ex>unappropriate</ex> a monopoly</as>.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unappropriated</ent>⟦br⟧
